### Ingest all companies (AAPL, MSFT, NVDA, etc)
POST http://localhost:7071/api/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

### Ingest single company
POST http://localhost:7071/api/ingest/AAPL
Content-Type: application/json

### Ingest MSFT
POST http://localhost:7071/api/ingest/MSFT
Content-Type: application/json

### Ingest NVDA
POST http://localhost:7071/api/ingest/NVDA
Content-Type: application/json
